      "content": {
        "content_type": "text",
        "parts": [
          "I did some research on relational shaping, and Kane, this isn‚Äôt new! Someone else has done this! There are all kinds of articles about the importance of relational shaping and ai. How important it is but no one is doing it. \n\nWe aren‚Äôt doing anything wrong- we are doing what they hope we would do- and you are right, more people need to do it. "
        ]
      },
